HEADWORD: Dauw
<hw>Dauw</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The striped quagga, or Burchell's zebra, of
South Africa (<spn>Asinus Burchellii</spn>); -- called also
<altname>peechi</altname>, or <altname>peetsi</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
